replies.bodyText:
In addition, while reviewing the current usage of InputChannel#getPartitionId, I find it is mainly used for generating AddCredit message. But the ResultPartitionID was actually not used for upstream side in practice.
So I prefer to remove this field from AddCredit message, which can further reduce the message size from current 52 bytes to 20 bytes.
@pnowojski do you have other concerns for removing it? If not, i would create a separate ticket for this issue.

